<li>Thinking of you and your family during this difficult time.  Your brother will be dearly missed.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry to hear about the passing of your brother. He was such a kind and loving person.</li>
<li>Words cannot express how saddened I am by your loss.  Please accept my heartfelt sympathy.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you mourn the loss of your beloved brother.</li>
<li>May the memories of your brother bring you peace and solace in the days ahead.</li>
<li>Your brother's warmth and kindness will be deeply missed by all who knew him.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, I offer my heartfelt condolences on the loss of your brother.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry for your loss.  May his soul rest in peace.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincerest condolences on the loss of your brother.  Sending love and support.</li>
<li>Your brother was a special person, and his memory will live on in the hearts of those who loved him.</li>
<li>Sending thoughts of peace and comfort to you and your family.</li>
<li>May the love and support of those around you help you through this difficult time.</li>
<li>I will always remember your brother's [mention a positive quality, e.g., infectious laughter].</li>
<li>Holding you and your family close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
    

